sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Data Scientist<br/>(Notebook / Workbench)
    participant SDK as CodeFlare SDK<br/>(Python Client)
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant KubeRay as KubeRay Operator
    participant RayHead as Ray Head Node<br/>8265/TCP Dashboard<br/>10001/TCP Client
    participant Router as OpenShift Router<br/>/ K8s Ingress

    Note over User,RayHead: Flow 1: Cluster Creation

    User->>SDK: Cluster(ClusterConfiguration(...))
    SDK->>K8sAPI: GET kueue.x-k8s.io/v1beta1/localqueues<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>SDK: LocalQueue list (validate queue)
    SDK->>SDK: Generate RayCluster YAML<br/>from base-template.yaml
    alt AppWrapper enabled
        SDK->>SDK: Wrap in AppWrapper CR
        SDK->>K8sAPI: POST workload.codeflare.dev/v1beta2/appwrappers<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        K8sAPI-->>SDK: AppWrapper created
    else Direct RayCluster
        SDK->>K8sAPI: POST ray.io/v1/rayclusters<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        K8sAPI-->>SDK: RayCluster created
    end
    KubeRay->>K8sAPI: Watch ray.io/v1/rayclusters
    KubeRay->>KubeRay: Reconcile → Create Ray Pods

    Note over User,RayHead: Flow 2: Job Submission

    User->>SDK: cluster.job_client.submit_job(...)
    SDK->>K8sAPI: GET route.openshift.io/v1/routes<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>SDK: Route → dashboard URL
    SDK->>Router: GET dashboard URL<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS
    Router-->>SDK: Redirect to Ray Head
    SDK->>RayHead: POST /api/jobs/<br/>8265/TCP HTTP/HTTPS<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (OpenShift)
    RayHead-->>SDK: Job ID
    loop Monitor Status
        SDK->>RayHead: GET /api/jobs/{id}<br/>8265/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
        RayHead-->>SDK: Job status + logs
    end

    Note over User,RayHead: Flow 3: TLS Certificate Generation

    User->>SDK: generate_tls_cert(cluster_name)
    SDK->>K8sAPI: GET secrets/{cluster_name}-ca-secret-*<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>SDK: CA key + CA cert
    SDK->>SDK: Generate client cert<br/>(RSA 2048 + SHA256)<br/>using cryptography library
    SDK->>SDK: Set RAY_TLS_* env vars
    User->>SDK: ray.init("ray://...")
    SDK->>RayHead: Connect 10001/TCP<br/>mTLS (client cert + CA)
    RayHead-->>SDK: Ray client session established

    Note over User,RayHead: Flow 4: Cluster Teardown

    User->>SDK: cluster.down()
    alt AppWrapper mode
        SDK->>K8sAPI: DELETE workload.codeflare.dev/v1beta2/appwrappers/{name}<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    else Direct mode
        SDK->>K8sAPI: DELETE ray.io/v1/rayclusters/{name}<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    end
    K8sAPI-->>SDK: Resource deleted
    KubeRay->>KubeRay: Cleanup Ray Pods
